&lt;p&gt;🎒 Buckles gleam, my leather pack; for adventures, there and back...&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;here-we-go-again-inktober-2024&quot;&gt;Here we go again! ...Inktober 2024&lt;&#x2F;h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So for this years inktober I&#x27;m planing to create artworks that I can use in my &lt;a href=&quot;&#x2F;projects&#x2F;quest&#x2F;&quot;&gt;Ultimate Quest&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; project. The prompts this year are all adventuring vibes so it actually coincides really nicely!&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;




&lt;img alt=&quot;Inktober 2024 prompt list&quot; title=&quot;Inktober 2024 prompt list&quot; src=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;inktober-2024-prompts.8bc5c078ac13548e.webp&quot; srcset=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;inktober-2024-prompts.b7728e63da828cd7.webp 512w, https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;inktober-2024-prompts.8bc5c078ac13548e.webp 1024w&quot; class=&quot;small framed&quot; &#x2F;&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I had planned to upgrade &lt;a href=&quot;&#x2F;projects&#x2F;deckorator&#x2F;&quot;&gt;Deckorator&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; to add SVG support (inspired by my recent work on &lt;a href=&quot;&#x2F;projects&#x2F;stickers&#x2F;&quot;&gt;Pop Snap&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;). Then each day I would post a finished game card but time has been stretched recently and I haven&#x27;t managed to get around to it. I&#x27;ve set myself a challenge to get that tool created by the end of Inktober 2024, -let&#x27;s see if I manage to make it ...I have some pretty awesome plans! 👀&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
</description>
      </item>
